OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FTurning
OL,6,Fcloudy across all parts through the
OL,7,Fevening with outbreaks of mainly light
OL,8,Frain spreading east overnight. More
OL,9,Fpersistent rain with some heavier
OL,10,Fbursts likely in the far west around
OL,11,Fdawn, especially over western hills.
OL,12,
OL,13,CMonday:FA band of rain, with embedded
OL,14,Fheavier pulses, spreads east during
OL,15,Fthe morning. Brighter conditions
OL,16,Ffollow but scattered, possibly
OL,17,Fthundery showers develop, though these
OL,18,Ftending to ease by late afternoon.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
