OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:
OL,6,FSunshine and showers Tuesday and
OL,7,FWednesday with a risk of hail and
OL,8,Fthunder. A fine start likely on
OL,9,FThursday, then rain arriving later.
OL,10,FBreezy at times and rather cool
OL,11,Foverall.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
